							}
						}
					],
					"documentation": "# Show Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Seller* inserts a Sale **key**.\n2. *System* displays the information associated to a **Sale** with this *saleNumber* **key** (**title**, **description**, **status**, **price**,**publicationDate** and **file**).  \n3. If the **buyer** wants to buy the **sale** extends **Buy**\n\n## Alternative flow\n1. If there is any attribute with no value, the field will be empty."
				},
				{
					"_type": "UMLActor",
					"_id": "AAAAAAGcHfSpFtexAQE=",
					"_parent": {
						"$ref": "AAAAAAGMFaB678SNc/w="
					},
					"name": "User",
